Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千砂 记得有次我跟你一起回过家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前说的那些话 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 死其实很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单得很
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你手上就拿着那种工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险栓已经打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扳机很重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两手紧握 用拇指摁住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女孩子来说要费点力气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在留恋现实世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初可是你叫我来这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体只是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想在明天放学后安排你们会面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男生挺帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要爱丽丝你有了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和老师的那个传言就会不攻自破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天再详谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实传言也没假…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有偷窥爱丽丝的隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没把爱丽丝的秘密散布在连线世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲音你干的 我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎不止一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是另一个我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许爱丽丝你也不止一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便我怎样辩解 你也不会相信我了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我会让一切都变成从未发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为办到这点 我一直在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不需要任何设备了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:19:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连线世界和现实世界的交界线 似乎已经被我破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我可以随心所欲地去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我此刻才会出现在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发生的事应该也能变成从未发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕…
